Package gen

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultRealizer
    This helper class provides, for each vertex, the default realizations described in Section 5 (Implementation) of the thesis.
    FirstStageProcessor
    This class implements the transition system for the first stage defined in the thesis; i.e., it handles MERGE, SWAP, DELETE and KEEP transitions.
    GoldSyntacticAnnotations
    A static class that contains functions to get the gold syntactic annotations for vertices.
    GoldTransitions
    A static class that contains functions to get the gold transitions to be applied to a vertex.
    Hyperparam
    This class is used to represent a hyperparameter used in the generation pipeline.
    Hyperparams
    This class stores all hyperparameters used in the generation pipeline.
    IntHyperparam
    This class is used to represent a special kind of hyperparameter that allows only integer values (see Hyperparam for more details).
    PartialTransitionFunction
    A naive implementation of a partial transition function as described in the thesis.
    PositionHelper
    This class provides methods to compute the probability of a REORDER transition and to get the takeBestN-best REORDER transitions as defined in the thesis (Section 4.2.1 Modeling).
    PostProcessor
    This class performs post-processing as described in the thesis.
    SecondStageProcessor
    This class implements the transition system for the second stage defined in the thesis; i.e., it handles all transitions but MERGE, SWAP, DELETE and KEEP.
